tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
    survey_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    consultation_date DATE NOT NULL,
    satisfaction_score INT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ConsultationQuality (
    consultation_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    doctor_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    consultation_date DATE NOT NULL,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    quality_rating INT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    consultation_id INT,
    rating INT,
    comments VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE virtual_consultation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    consultation_date DATE,
    doctor_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    consultation_feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE virtual_consultations (
    consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    consultation_date DATE,
    consultation_time TIME,
    consultation_duration INT
);
